each riddle must be in each file in this directory with .rdl extension. all other extensions will be ignored.
first line in riddle file must be riddle answer, second line - riddle description, third line - first hint, fourth line - second hint, fifth line - number of allowed attempts
example:
"
Apple
A fruit that can be red, green, or yellow
It's famous for keeping doctors away
Snow White was poisoned with one
3
"